author: Rishiraj Acharya
title: Great pen just for unboxing!
content:
Very nice pen with an elegant classy matte finish which really looks premium. The writing is one of the smoothest in metal pens.
Downsides are that the black finish will fade away much faster than you would even expect and the refill is really hard to find in markets.
Also I got the pen for just ₹ 112 and I am kinda happy how you have to pay the full ₹ 150 cost! cry a little!
